                    Hello from SHKOLA!



We are an international bilingual online school for kids 7-18 years old.



Our mission is to support every child to prepare for a successful and happy future.



We are looking for a native-speaking, enthusiastic and inspiring teacher, who can teach children English through educational games, and exciting and well-thought lessons. If that sounds like you — we are looking forward to your application!



Responsibilities:



- Teach children at age of 7-18;

- Provide high-quality online lessons;

- Assess a student’s English level and provide a feedback;

- Enjoy classes!



Requirements:



- English native speakers or bilinguals;

- TEFL\CELTA certification (specialization for children) is preferable;

- Experience (or Degree) in teaching Maths is obligatory;

- Communicative and gaming techniques for individual and group lessons;

- Online working experience is preferable.



Job Benefits:

- Full-time contracts;

- Fixed schedule with no less than 20 hours per week;

- International supportive team;

- Professional trainings are provided;

- Financial detailed can be discussed during the interview.
